♪Need to smooth out the temper♪

211
00:10:26,465 --> 00:10:33,487
♪Need words that are crafted finely♪

212
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:40,631
♪Need to remember the premise♪

213
00:10:41,473 --> 00:10:45,220
♪Conceal the candid but harsh advice♪

214
00:10:46,424 --> 00:10:48,438
♪In the heart♪

215
00:10:51,327 --> 00:10:56,669
♪Need to practice repeatedly♪

216
00:10:58,337 --> 00:11:05,263
♪With limbs that make a deafening noise♪

217
00:11:06,209 --> 00:11:11,385
♪How should I bring it up♪

218
00:11:13,316 --> 00:11:19,029
♪What kind of topic should I seek♪

219
00:11:21,185 --> 00:11:26,378
♪How should I make the analogy♪

220
00:11:28,353 --> 00:11:36,068
♪Is that love concern
or a torture device♪

221
00:11:36,068 --> 00:11:37,749
♪Please♪

222
00:11:39,489 --> 00:11:41,572
♪Don't♪

223
00:11:43,201 --> 00:11:45,273
♪Recall♪

224
00:12:13,636 --> 00:12:19,236
♪Don't forget♪
